===Etymology===
Contracted from ‘'''[[blind]] [[me]]!'''’ or ‘'''[[blame]] [[me]]'''’. <!-- so as not to seem like [[blasphemy]]; in [[medieval]] times, people would curse using [[contractions]] rather than breaking the [[w:Ten commandments|third commandment]] (Do not use the Lord's name in [[vain]] [[oath]]s).--> Compare '''[['sblood]]''', '''[[strewth]]''', '''[[zounds]]''', etc.

